{"filename":"linux_bash_alias.adoc","rendered":"<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\">\n<div id=\"toctitle\">目次</div>\n<ul class=\"sectlevel1\">\n<li><a href=\"#_結論\">☕結論</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div id=\"preamble\">\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<table class=\"tableblock frame-all grid-all fit-content\">\n<caption class=\"title\">Table 1. 環境</caption>\n<colgroup>\n<col>\n<col>\n</colgroup>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"tableblock halign-left valign-top\">App</th>\n<th class=\"tableblock halign-left valign-top\">Version</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"tableblock halign-left valign-top\"><p class=\"tableblock\"><strong>Debian</strong></p></td>\n<td class=\"tableblock halign-left valign-top\"><p class=\"tableblock\"><em>11</em></p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"tableblock halign-left valign-top\"><p class=\"tableblock\"><strong>bash</strong></p></td>\n<td class=\"tableblock halign-left valign-top\"><p class=\"tableblock\"><em>5.1.4</em></p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_結論\">☕結論</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"admonitionblock important\">\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"icon\">\n<i class=\"fa icon-important\" title=\"Important\" data-md-icon=\"report\"></i>\n</td>\n<td class=\"content\">\nエイリアスは <code>~/.bash_aliases</code> ファイルに記述すればいい。\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><code>~/.bashrc</code> では下記の記述があり、<code>~/.bash_aliases</code> を読み込んでいる。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"quoteblock\">\n<blockquote>\n<div \n    class=\"listingblock\">\n\n  <div class=\"content\">\n  <pre class=\"highlight \" ><code class=\"language-bash\"\n    data-lang=\"bash\"># Alias definitions.\n# You may want to put all your additions into a separate file like\n# ~/.bash_aliases, instead of adding them here directly.\n# See /usr/share/doc/bash-doc/examples in the bash-doc package.\n\nif [ -f ~/.bash_aliases ]; then\n    . ~/.bash_aliases\nfi</code></pre>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"attribution\">\n&#8212; ~/.bashrc\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"exampleblock\">\n<div class=\"title\">Example 1. Bash エイリアスの記述例</div>\n<div class=\"content\">\n<div \n    class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"title\">~/.bash_aliases</div>\n  <div class=\"content\">\n  <pre class=\"highlight \" ><code class=\"language-bash\"\n    data-lang=\"bash\">alias git='podman run --rm -it --mount type=bind,src=\"$(pwd)\",dst=/git alpine/git:v2.32.0'</code></pre>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","title":"Bash エイリアスを記述する設定ファイルってどれ？","created_at":"2022-02-18","tags":["bash","alias","備忘録"],"author":"v1.0, 2022-02-18"}